{"word":"κηρίον","slug":"κηρίον","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κηρίον</b></el> <el>(κηρίον, ου, τό,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:κηρός'><el>κηρός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a honeycomb</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>favus</el>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; also, <el>κηρίον σφηκῶν</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a wax tablet</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}